715005f-b.title: Manhattan: 108th Street (West) - Columbus Avenue
715005f-b.text:
(1)
127-129 West 108th Street, north side, between Columbus and
Amsterdam Aves. These are both 3--story frame houses.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 343.
